I solved it using Projections:

    @Value(&quot;#{@userService.getUpdatedByUserName(target)}&quot;)
    String getUpdatedByUserName();

`userService` is the name of the UserService Spring Bean in this case.

See the [Spring Data JPA Docs][1], Example 91


  [1]: https://docs.spring.io/spring-data/jpa/docs/current/reference/html/#projections

